hi từ kỳ 03 - 竹枝詞其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/author-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Vương Quang Duẫn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%C4%83ng/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi/poem-cpSKaf4G94fF9ZzvStESWA">Trương Chi - 張芝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%C4%83ng/author-o7Hf6CJEKu5UA5pXP2ZmbA">Nguyễn Hữu Thăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-T%C3%B4ng-ph%C3%B9-nh%C6%B0-h%C3%A0/poem-vUmsfNq4mE-rL0etWalB4A">Vọng nhạc (Đại Tông phù như hà) - 望嶽（岱宗夫如何）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Bi%E1%BB%87n-Vinh/Xu%C3%A2n-du-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-qH6rn0jHIxGzKVbzbRlRJA">Xuân du đồ - 春遊圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Bi%E1%BB%87n-Vinh/author-QKyM7SoFCzI5hQwR-YTzUA">Biện Vinh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
